    medical_ai "Worker 477. Your latest health metrics indicate respiratory function at 71%% baseline. This is within acceptable parameters. If function drops below 60%%, please report for evaluation."
    narrator "Seventy-one percent. When did it drop below eighty? When did I stop noticing?"
